  <?dbhtml filename="xineramaproto.html"?>

  <title>xineramaproto-&xineramaproto-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This is an X extension that allows multiple physical screens controlled by
      a single X server to appear as a single screen.
    </para>

